column2: SELECT s.plate, s.fiberid, s.mjd, g.petroRad_g,                           g.petroRad_u,g.petroRad_r,g.petroRad_i,                           g.petroRad_z, sph.z,sph.dered_u, sph.dered_g,                           sph.dered_i, sph.dered_r, sph.dered_z                     FROM  specobj as s, Galaxy as g, SpecPhoto as sph                       WHERE s.class = &&&                          AND s.specobjid = g.specobjid                           AND sph.specobjid = g.specobjid                          AND g.specobjid > #                          AND sph.z > # into MyDB.test
